    "As the emergence of Web3 unfolds, multiple platforms aim to provide similar services.",
    "Identifying the platform that will prevail in the long run is challenging.",
    "Ethereum may be the MSN in this scenario, but who will be the WhatsApp?",
    "It's not a single platform; projects like NEAR and SOL, among others, offer comparable functionalities to Ethereum.",
    "The long-term viability of crypto projects depends on their ability to deliver unique services and align with user preferences."
